UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 2454
1 Section 3. The Senate encourages all Kentuckians to support early detection,
2 raise awareness, and participate in programs that provide emotional and practical support
3 to those affected by breast cancer.
4 Section 4. The Clerk of the Senate is directed to transmit a copy of this
5 Resolution to Senator Julie Raque Adams for delivery to the Board of Directors of Hope
6 in the Fight KY.
